Package: leanclust
Title: Student Performance Clustering and Classification
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Sertan", "SAFAK", , "setosfk@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides lean and efficient clustering algorithms to analyze 
    student data. It automatically evaluates and assigns students into 
    specific performance classes based on their academic success within 
    their respective classrooms. Designed for fast and reproducible 
    educational data mining.
